      "text": "Packet Replay\n• Reads PCAP,  stamps DSCP into IP header based on sender identity\n• Wraps each IP packet in a frame and sends to engine\n over a TCP socket:  [8B sim timestamp] [2B length] [IP packet bytes]\n",
