      "text": "Queue w/ CPU priority sort\n───────────\nstd::sort  (introsort,  O(n log n))\nBuffer: per-scenario\nLink: 45 Gbps\nPriority: DSCP 46 = ctrl\nBlind window =\nmeasured sort time\n45 µs (low) -> 4 222 µs (high)\nScales with batch size",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
