      "updated": 1776999600000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Spec                        CPU FIFO                   CPU PQ                          GPU PQ\n────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nSort algorithm              none  (drop-tail FIFO)      introsort  O(n log n)            Thrust radix sort  O(d·n)\nEviction policy             FIFO  (no priority)         evict lowest-priority bulk       evict lowest-priority bulk\nBlind window  (low)         none                        45 µs                            34 µs\nBlind window  (medium)      none                        956 µs                           51 µs\nBlind window  (high)        none                        4 222 µs                         70 µs\nCtrl drop %   (low)         0%                          0%                               0%\nCtrl drop %   (medium)      61.3%                       22.3%                            7.8%\nCtrl drop %   (high)        65.1%                       50.0%                            16.9%\nGPU features                —                           —                                pinned mem (cudaHostAlloc)  ·  3 async CUDA streams  ·  warm-up sort\nBuffer                      per-scenario                per-scenario                     per-scenario\nBottleneck link             45 Gbps  ·  1 µs            45 Gbps  ·  1 µs                 45 Gbps  ·  1 µs",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Spec                        CPU FIFO                   CPU PQ                          GPU PQ\n────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nSort algorithm              none  (drop-tail FIFO)      introsort  O(n log n)            Thrust radix sort  O(d·n)\nEviction policy             FIFO  (no priority)         evict lowest-priority bulk       evict lowest-priority bulk\nBlind window  (low)         none                        45 µs                            34 µs\nBlind window  (medium)      none                        956 µs                           51 µs\nBlind window  (high)        none                        4 222 µs                         70 µs\nCtrl drop %   (low)         0%                          0%                               0%\nCtrl drop %   (medium)      61.3%                       22.3%                            7.8%\nCtrl drop %   (high)        65.1%                       50.0%                            16.9%\nGPU features                —                           —                                pinned mem (cudaHostAlloc)  ·  3 async CUDA streams  ·  warm-up sort\nBuffer                      per-scenario                per-scenario                     per-scenario\nBottleneck link             45 Gbps  ·  1 µs            45 Gbps  ·  1 µs                 45 Gbps  ·  1 µs",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "ao",
      "autoResize": false
    }
